With four policemen hustling his hunched body onto the street, Assange protested the admission of British officers to Ecuadorian diplomatic territory.
In my own dealings with Assange, he has often overstated his abilities as a hacker; he is a self-confessed dissembler.
That the indictment leaned so heavily on this document shows just how far the Trump Administration had to go to build a case against Assange.
Assange, a devoted opponent of what he describes as American imperial power, has welcomed Trump’s degradation of U.S. norms and institutions.
“Resist this attempt by the Trump Administration!”